<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">هِشَامٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> إِذَا اغْتَسَلَ مِنَ الْجَنَابَةِ غَسَلَ يَدَهُ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>